ABAP Statements

 My first simple program in ABAP:
PARAMETERS pa_num TYPE i .
DATA gv_result TYPE i .
MOVE pa_num TO gv_result .
ADD l TO gv_result .
WRITE 'Your input: ' .
WRITE pa_num .
NEW-LINE .
WRITE 'Result:     ' .
WRITE gv_result .
